---
import Container from "./container.astro";
import Sectionhead from "./sectionhead.astro";
---

<Container>
  <Sectionhead>
    <Fragment slot="title">Official Tournament Rules</Fragment>
    <Fragment slot="desc">Award ceremony to follow the conclusion of the final round on Sunday.</Fragment>
  </Sectionhead>

  <div class=" max-w-xl mx-auto mt-8">
    <div class="mt-4 mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Scoring System</h2>
      <div>1. Modified Stableford scoring will be used for each round.</div>
      <div>2. The player with the most points at the end of all tournament rounds will be declared the winner.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="mt-4 mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Handicap</h2>
        <div>100% of each player's handicap will be applied up to a maximum of 30.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="mt-4 mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Tiebreaker</h2>
      <div>In the event of a tie for first place after the completion of all rounds, a putting competition will be held immediately following the final round to determine the winner.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="mt-4 mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Additional Rules</h2>
      <div>1. All other standard golf rules apply as per the R&A and USGA.</div>
      <div>2. Once a player reaches net double bogey on a hole, they should pick-up their ball to maintain pace of play.</div>
      <div>3. Players must record and submit their scores after each round.</div>
      <div>4. Paper scorecards must be attested, signed, and turned in at the end of each round.</div>
      <div>5. Any disputes will be resolved by the tournament committee, whose decision will be final.</div>
    </div>
    
    <!-- STABLEFORD SCORING SECTION -->
    <div class="mt-4 mb-8">
  <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Modified Stableford Scoring</h2>
  <table class="w-full text-left border-collapse">
    <thead>
      <tr class="border-b-2 border-gray-300">
        <th class="py-2 pr-4">Result</th>
        <th class="py-2 pr-4">Net to Par</th>
        <th class="py-2">Points</th>
      </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr class="border-b border-gray-200">
        <td class="py-2 pr-4">Double Eagle</td>
        <td class="py-2 pr-4">-3</td>
        <td class="py-2">8</td>
      </tr>
      <tr class="border-b border-gray-200">
        <td class="py-2 pr-4">Eagle</td>
        <td class="py-2 pr-4">-2</td>
        <td class="py-2">5</td>
      </tr>
      <tr class="border-b border-gray-200">
        <td class="py-2 pr-4">Birdie</td>
        <td class="py-2 pr-4">-1</td>
        <td class="py-2">2</td>
      </tr>
      <tr class="border-b border-gray-200">
        <td class="py-2 pr-4">Par</td>
        <td class="py-2 pr-4">E</td>
        <td class="py-2">1</td>
      </tr>
      <tr class="border-b border-gray-200">
        <td class="py-2 pr-4">Bogey</td>
        <td class="py-2 pr-4">+1</td>
        <td class="py-2">0</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td class="py-2 pr-4">Double Bogey or more</td>
        <td class="py-2 pr-4">+2 or more</td>
        <td class="py-2">-2</td>
      </tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>
</div>
  
  </div>
</Container>
